    "instructions": [
        [{
            "step": "Wash and chop **lettuce** into bite sized pieces. Wash and chop **scallions** to rounds. Peel and mince **garlic cloves**.",
            "context": [
                {
                    "category": "recommendation",
                    "note": "If serving with rice, wash and cook rice first. Keep rice warm until ready to serve"
                }
            ]
        }],
        [{
            "step": "Combine **oyster sauce**, **soy sauce**, and **sugar** in a bowl. Mix well"
        }],
        [{
            "step": "- In a pan, heat up **neutral oil** over high heat until slightly smoking. Add **minced garlic**, **chopped scallion**, and **red pepper flakes** and fry until aromatic.\n  - Add **combined sauce** to pan. Add **water** to deglaze pan and to adjust for consistency. Cook until sauce is thickened. Pour sauce out and set aside."
        }],
        [{
            "step": "In the same pan, boil slightly salted water. Once boiled, add **chopped lettuce** and cook until leaves turn bright green. Remove from pan and strain."
        }],
        [{
            "step": "Serve **lettuce** with **sauce** drizzled on top."
